                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200628-147-off808 t18200628-147-crimeloc810"></join>. I let the prisoner a furnished lodging, at 3 s. a week. He remained four weeks, and left on the 20th of June without notice. I found the door open, and missed the sheets and blanket. He was apprehended that evening. Another man, whom he recommended to me, lodged with him, and both left together - he occupied another room.</p>
